  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >背景</h2> 为了拯救多多丛林的被毒蛇咬伤的老猴王，王子悠悠风与他的小伙伴悠悠智一起穿越神秘的大峡谷、平原、雪山，齐心协力，克服困难，拿到圣雪莲！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >摆动</h2>控制手臂，利用惯性，摆动前进！小心坠落~（碰到尖刺也会受伤，要重新开始哦！）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590420/extras/38abb159f81c0b4fea2ed2611c463c56.poster.avif?t=1621496091\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590420/extras/38abb159f81c0b4fea2ed2611c463c56.webm?t=1621496091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590420/extras/38abb159f81c0b4fea2ed2611c463c56.mp4?t=1621496091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >机关—蹦床</h2>下落~弹跳！充分利用弹跳的高度，快速的抵达目标地点！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590420/extras/d4511da0c19b012ca05aed88280ec9fd.poster.avif?t=1621496091\" width=620 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590420/extras/d4511da0c19b012ca05aed88280ec9fd.webm?t=1621496091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590420/extras/d4511da0c19b012ca05aed88280ec9fd.mp4?t=1621496091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >机关—易碎石块</h2>极其脆弱的平台，无法长时间的停留，抓紧时间通过吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590420/extras/2916d291a64b9d46e7728bc08b8ad765.poster.avif?t=1621496091\" width=620 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590420/extras/2916d291a64b9d46e7728bc08b8ad765.webm?t=1621496091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590420/extras/2916d291a64b9d46e7728bc08b8ad765.mp4?t=1621496091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>还有许多关卡、机关等待挑战，为了取得圣雪莲而努力！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590420/extras/4b15a1a1014c1e2edb00649f5ee581e1.avif?t=1621496091\" width=348 height=410 /></span><br><br><br><a href=\"mailto:相关合作请联系：mengxy@haimio.com\">相关合作请联系：mengxy@haimio.com</a>",
